Project_Title: The miRNA expression of exosome secreted by human urine-derived stem cells (human)
Project_Description:
We identify miRNA profiles from exosomes of human urine-derived stem cells (USCs).
Overall design: We hypothesized that miRNAs in the human urine-derived stem cells (USCs)-derived exosomes contributed to the vaginal epithelial cells through exosome transfer. MiRNA microarray analysis was performed on exosomes secreted by human USCs cells.
